41:50.435 --> 41:52.369
Amy: (Amused) Okay...

41:52.404 --> 41:56.206
Are you taking a trip... to the 1960s?

41:56.240 --> 41:59.343
Ty: Uh, no.
I told Caleb I burned his cheque

41:59.377 --> 42:00.944
