42:04.416 --> 42:06.883
Amy: What?! Oh my... (Money bundles rustle)

42:06.918 --> 42:09.219
Are you serious?!

42:09.253 --> 42:11.188
Ty: Yeah, I'm serious. Look at it all.

42:11.222 --> 42:13.856
- Not too shabby, huh?
- Amy: Not too shabby at all.

42:13.890 --> 42:16.125
So... what-what is your plan?

42:16.159 --> 42:18.127
What're you gonna do with all this?

42:18.161 --> 42:20.863
Ty: Wrong question.

42:20.897 --> 42:23.232
We're about to get married, right?

42:23.266 --> 42:25.600
So the right question is,
what're we gonna do with this...

42:25.635 --> 42:27.469
(Kiss)

42:27.503 --> 42:29.271
- Ty: Together?
- Amy: Right.

42:29.306 --> 42:33.074
What are we gonna do with this?

42:33.108 --> 42:36.244
Ty: (Whispers) I have no idea.
Amy: (Laughs)

42:36.278 --> 42:38.870
- Ty: (Laughing) Woo-hoo!
- Amy: (Laughing hysterically)

